cOS","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b6d7/67d2/22_mini.png?m=1649080598","stars":5109,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":22,"parent_node_name":"os"},"member":{"id":665733,"username":"jonathanmartinez","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/jonathanmartinez","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/0a315fb1f08442685c8f26b403b8b6d9?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/0a315fb1f08442685c8f26b403b8b6d9?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/0a315fb1f08442685c8f26b403b8b6d9?s=73&d=retro","created":1701752357,"last_modified":1705125053},"last_reply_by":"imnpc","last_touched":1705133802,"title":"mac 端 QQ 音乐拿着用户的带宽当 CDN","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/1008319","created":1705125380,"deleted":0,"content":"今天发现 istat menus 显示有一直比较大的上传速度, 最高有 10MB/s, 我想着自己本地没开什么上传的服务, 点开一看是 QQ 音乐一直在上传, 于是打开防火墙小飞贼一看, QQ 音乐的 ip 连接数有 15000 多了, 上传流量达到了 65GB, 小飞贼卡的都点不动了.....","content_rendered":"今天发现 istat menus 显示有一直比较大的上传速度, 最高有 10MB/s, 我想着自己本地没开什么上传的服务, 点开一看是 QQ 音乐一直在上传, 于是打开防火墙小飞贼一看, QQ 音乐的 ip 连接数有 15000 多了, 上传流量达到了 65GB, 小飞贼卡的都点不动了.....","last_modified":1705125380,"replies":25,"id":1008319},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340","name":"qna","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340","title":"问与答","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","topics":214180,"footer":"","header":"一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。","title_alternative":"Questions and Answers","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","stars":4070,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":12,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"id":654183,"username":"batchfy","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/batchfy","website":"batchfy.com","twitter":"batchfy","psn":"","github":"batchfy","btc":"","location":"USA","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/ac65b1d0d9200bb89bcf387cd1342052?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/ac65b1d0d9200bb89bcf387cd1342052?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/ac65b1d0d9200bb89bcf387cd1342052?s=73&d=retro","created":1696994318,"last_modified":1696994318},"last_reply_by":"iseki","last_touched":1705133380,"title":"RESTFul 后端返回什么 HTTP 状态码比较规范","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/1008308","created":1705120667,"deleted":0,"content":"请问 RESTFul 后端响应的 HTTP 状态码应该是什么比较规范？\r\n\r\n我们现在是全部返回`200`，只有后台挂了，或者是代理错误前端才会受到错误码\r\n\r\n比如登录的账号密码错了，api 会返回 status=200 ，并在 body 部分返回错误码和 message 。\r\n或者查找用户，用户不存在，也会返回 200 ，并在 body 部分返回错误信息。\r\n\r\n\r\n我们决定这么做的原因是 **能够通过状态码区分是 CDN/代理的错误，还是后台挂了。只要状态码是 200 ，就说明后台没挂**。\r\n\r\n___\r\n我参考了几个网站，发现他们的 api 如果操作错误，会响应具有语义的状态码。比如查找不存在，会返回 404 ；登录密码错误，会返回 5XX 。\r\n___\r\n\r\n请问这种实现规范么？有没有什么可以参考的？\r\n\r\n\r\n请大家指教，谢谢！","content_rendered":"<p>请问 RESTFul 后端响应的 HTTP 状态码应该是什么比较规范？</p>\n<p>我们现在是全部返回<code>200</code>，只有后台挂了，或者是代理错误前端才会受到错误码</p>\n<p>比如登录的账号密码错了，api 会返回 status=200 ，并在 body 部分返回错误码和 message 。\n或者查找用户，用户不存在，也会返回 200 ，并在 body 部分返回错误信息。</p>\n<p>我们决定这么做的原因是 <strong>能够通过状态码区分是 CDN/代理的错误，还是后台挂了。只要状态码是 200 ，就说明后台没挂</strong>。</p>\n<hr/>\n<p>我参考了几个网站，发现他们的 api 如果操作错误，会响应具有语义的状态码。比如查找不存在，会返回 404 ；登录密码错误，会返回 5XX 。</p>\n<hr/>\n<p>请问这种实现规范么？有没有什么可以参考的？</p>\n<p>请大家指教，谢谢！</p>\n","last_modified":1705120667,"replies":18,"id":1008308},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9f0/f895/8_large.png?m=1630643991","name":"iphone","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9f0/f895/8_normal.png?m=1630643991","title":"iPhone","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/iphone","topics":11107,"footer":"这里绝不讨论如何获得 iPhone 盗版软件、iTunes 黑卡之类。","header":"Say hello to the future.","title_alternative":"iPhone","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9f0/f895/8_mini.png?m=1630643991","stars":3312,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":8,"parent_node_name":"apple"},"member":{"id":503696,"username":"Babbitt","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Babbitt","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":